				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$V_{{oc}}$$\end{document}), short-circuit current density (Jsc\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
