				\begin{document}$$P_{m}$$\end{document}), PCE and fill factor (FF). Although the high thickness of the did\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
