We used a ZnO layer as ETL due to its high optical transmittance in the VR and NIR regions and high carrier mobility (0.066 cm2 V−1 s−1)58–60. We made the deposition of ZnO with the sputtering technique using a ZnO target with a purity of 99.999%. To get high optical transmittance, the thickness (detl)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
