				\begin{document}$$(d_{{etl}} )~$$\end{document} of ETL was set to 40 nm. We coated the active region of SCs with the spin coating technique using P3HT:PCBM. We prepared the solution from the ready-made P3HT and PCBM polymers by blending them evenly by means of mass and adding dichlorobenzene solvent at a concentration of 20 mg/mL. We allowed this to mix homogeneously with a magnetic stirrer for 14 h at 80 °C. For all OSCs, we set P3HT:PCBM active layer thickness (dal\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
